OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain affecting much of the region.
OL,8,FSome heavy bursts are likely across
OL,9,Fhigher ground. Rain clearing during
OL,10,Fearly hours. Gusty winds throughout.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FThursday remaining mostly
OL,13,Fdry and breezy, with some clear or
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Temperatures close to
OL,15,Faverage.
